  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read `docs/procedures/testing-and-code-quality.md` in full. Identify the code review checklist section (most likely heading: "Code Review", "Code Review Checklist", or similar).</step>
    <step order="2">If a checklist section exists, add the FR-24 line as a new bullet. If no checklist section exists, add a brief "Code Review" subsection containing this single bullet. The exact line:
