      - [ ] Verify test-update obligation per [`.claude/constraints/bff-extensions.md`](../../.claude/constraints/bff-extensions.md).
      ```
    </step>
    <step order="3">Apply the edit via the Edit tool. Preserve existing procedure sections.</step>
